'''Lî-pai-si''' (禮拜四), yú hêm-cho '''pai-si''' (拜四), '''sên-khì-si''' (星期四) lâu '''muk-yeu-ngit''' (木曜日), he yit-chiak [[sên-khì]] tú ke yit thiên, chhai [[lî-pai-sâm]] ke heu-mî, [[lî-pai-ńg]] ke thèu-chhièn.

Chhai [[Kî-tuk-kau]] ke vùn-fa tú, [[Yâ-fò-fà]] Sông-ti chhai pai-si chhóng-chho [[ngit-thèu]], [[ngie̍t-khiù|ngie̍t]] thiên sông-poi [[sên-è]].

